{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act18d3", "eventName": "覆潮之下", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "SV-8", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "親族", "storyInfo": "歌蕾蒂婭殺死了海嗣。主教憤怒地撲向深海獵人。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ibcave"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#3", "name2": "avg_npc_186"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_skill_skulsrsword", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘶——", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "海嗣的身體再一次被歌蕾蒂婭洞穿。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "海嗣將死。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "海嗣沒有把“臉”轉向主教。旁人也不可能知道海嗣是否長著眼睛，但斯卡蒂就是能感覺到怪物的視線——至少她自己這麼覺得。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "它正“看著”主教。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "無形的洋流正沖刷著主教，袍裙沉重地壓在他的身上，幾要把他摧垮。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "但海嗣正對她們說話。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#3", "name2": "avg_npc_186", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們是更像我......還是更像他？", "name": "海嗣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_186"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Gla-dia。 你很強壯。", "name": "海嗣"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_186"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "歌蕾蒂婭冰冷地注視著獵物。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "情緒。會有我們血親學習的。我們也在傳達許多，我們會試著傳達給你們。", "name": "海嗣"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Ishar-mla。活著吧。活著會很好。下一次會有其他血親找到你......向你詢問。", "name": "海嗣"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們不太會問問題。我們會學會。", "name": "海嗣"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5", "name2": "char_empty", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "慢慢地，海嗣低哼著蹲下去。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "怪物的軀體不再起伏。它蜷縮起來，像一朵迅速枯敗的花。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——死了。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "斯卡蒂如釋重負。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "不，不能這麼說。她並沒有從真相中恢復過來。但這個獵物的死讓她感受到......", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "它到底也只是個生物。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warchaos_intro", "key": "$warchaos_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_184"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們這些孽種。", "name": "主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_184"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "主教提高了音量。零碎的聲響在他的喉頭，在激烈戰鬥留下的碎屑中爬行，像是他的聲帶正不住嘟囔。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "歌蕾蒂婭甚至沒去看他。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是，上前來。現在輪到你。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這隻垃圾孑然一身。外面那些恐魚也不是它這族的。那麼，只會是你的了。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_184"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我來把你們撕碎。我來讓你們褻瀆的行徑受罰。", "name": "主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_184"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我自己來。是得在這裡把你們這些雜種都解決掉。生命可貴，但留你們的命是浪費資源。", "name": "主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_184"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個重傷的孽種。一個動彈不得的孽種。我會把你們的殘渣抛灑在大地上，讓最低賤的陸地生物吃掉你們的一切。", "name": "主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_184"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "殺死你們兩個，輕而易舉——", "name": "主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_184"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用再裝了。比起海嗣這些垃圾，還是你們這種曾經是人，現在又偽裝成人的最讓人反胃。", "name": "歌蕾蒂婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_474_gladiia_1#5"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_184"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（嘶吼）", "name": "主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_184"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們會死在這裡！", "name": "主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_184"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是不是把我忘了？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1", "name2": "avg_474_gladiia_1#4"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "斯卡蒂翻了個白眼。歌蕾蒂婭笑了笑。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_184"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "主教遲疑了一下，轉過頭去。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}